01:53.297 --> 01:55.030
- Take it back.
- I can't take it back.

01:55.032 --> 01:56.564
- Take it back.
- I can't take it back.

01:56.566 --> 01:58.169
- Take it back.
- I can't.

01:59.469 --> 02:00.271
Joke's on you.

02:01.371 --> 02:04.106
