03:04.168 --> 03:05.935
The weather, it's nice.

03:05.937 --> 03:09.570
Oh, uh, sure.

03:09.572 --> 03:10.607
Gonna be hot.

03:12.410 --> 03:13.409
What?

03:13.411 --> 03:14.778
