03:23.220 --> 03:28.225
Well, I'm gonna go
inside, cause of the heat.

03:30.361 --> 03:32.794
Right, see you around, huh?

03:32.796 --> 03:33.630
Sure.

03:57.487 --> 03:59.054
Motherfu

03:59.056 --> 04:00.922
Barry Klein does little
more than spit out a line,

04:00.924 --> 04:02.890
as if he's reading a textbook.

04:02.892 --> 04:06.963
