is mind-numbingly dull.

04:08.299 --> 04:11.400
But where Barry Klein is
lacking in his performance,

04:11.402 --> 04:14.103
it's made up for
by the true stars

04:14.105 --> 04:15.970
of the Austin Theater community,

04:15.972 --> 04:19.241
