04:27.984 --> 04:29.084
Heartwrenching?

04:29.086 --> 04:31.286
Babe, I'm proud of you, okay?

04:31.288 --> 04:33.422
Go out there tonight,
do your thing,

04:33.424 --> 04:35.290
and don't give a shit
about what anybody says,

04:35.292 --> 04:37.761
especially, Steven Dordoff?

