05:07.191 --> 05:08.257
Probably.

05:08.259 --> 05:09.358
Oh, but I don't like her.

05:09.360 --> 05:10.625
Well, you don't like anybody.

05:10.627 --> 05:11.993
Well I especially
don't like her.

05:11.995 --> 05:15.166
Me neither.

05:22.073 --> 05:23.037
- Whoa.
- Whoa, watch it!

05:23.039 --> 05:23.740
Jesus.

05:24.841 --> 05:26.674
Fuckin' Californians.

05:56.673 --> 05:57.508
Hey Susie.

05:58.542 --> 06:01.878
Hi Phyl, sorry I
didn't see you there.

06:05.014 --> 06:05.947
Is Jamie here?

06:05.949 --> 06:08.584
