06:34.878 --> 06:35.877
Thanks.

06:35.879 --> 06:38.247
I've been inspired recently.

06:38.249 --> 06:39.082
It shows.

06:40.817 --> 06:42.217
Whatcha readin'?

06:42.219 --> 06:43.052
A story.

06:44.588 --> 06:46.557
No shit, a story?

06:47.891 --> 06:48.725
Uh huh.

06:50.894 --> 06:52.429
What's it about?

06:53.663 --> 06:57.098
Okay, so this
couple's been together

06:57.100 --> 07:01.270
