an incurable blood disease,

07:01.272 --> 07:02.737
and she died.

07:02.739 --> 07:04.972
You know, sell a few of these
and you'll be a real artist.

07:04.974 --> 07:07.242
I am a real artist.

07:07.244 --> 07:09.777
What?

07:09.779 --> 07:14.784
Before that, her husband,
or boyfriend, or whatever,

07:17.254 --> 07:20.422
