the last days of her life.

07:23.760 --> 07:26.495
You know, with like,
the black and white,

07:26.497 --> 07:28.599
and the light, and shit?

07:30.634 --> 07:32.833
I have a house full
of art that I made

07:32.835 --> 07:34.035
with my own two hands.

07:34.037 --> 07:35.870
This is an actual piece
of art that I made,

07:35.872 --> 07:37.071
