half that effort into anything.

07:47.817 --> 07:49.284
I don't have time for this.

07:49.286 --> 07:50.851
I have a huge fucking
gallery opening tomorrow,

07:50.853 --> 07:52.119
which maybe you know
something about,

07:52.121 --> 07:54.389
because your art
is hanging in it.

07:54.391 --> 07:57.725
I have a shit ton of work
to do to get ready for it.

07:57.727 --> 08:00.895
All right, can I help you?

08:00.897 --> 08:03.132
Yeah, that would
actually be really great.

08:04.335 --> 08:05.802
Some girls just
have all the luck.

08:07.837 --> 08:08.838
But she's dead.

08:10.039 --> 08:10.873
Your point?

08:13.544 --> 08:15.577
Barry, what are
you doing here?

08:15.579 --> 08:17.548
Jamie, nice to see you.

08:19.583 --> 08:21.015
All right, don't be mad.

08:21.017 --> 08:22.216
What?

08:22.218 --> 08:24.087
I think I'm gonna stay here
and help with the opening.

08:25.855 --> 08:26.657
You sure?

08:27.691 --> 08:29.993
