vicious today.

08:30.827 --> 08:32.594
Yes, and yes.

08:32.596 --> 08:36.498
Okay, well, I would
offer to stay and help,

08:36.500 --> 08:39.934
but I hate her, and I
don't wanna do that.

08:39.936 --> 08:41.869
All right, break a leg.

08:41.871 --> 08:42.706
I'll try.

08:54.183 --> 08:55.182
Hey.

08:55.184 --> 08:56.017
Oh, hey Barry.

08:56.019 --> 08:57.184
