09:06.463 --> 09:07.562
Hey man.

09:07.564 --> 09:08.863
Hey, Barry.

09:08.865 --> 09:10.231
Did you see the review, man?

09:10.233 --> 09:12.033
Yeah, I saw the review.

09:12.035 --> 09:13.102
Damn, well,

09:14.705 --> 09:15.639
