09:30.387 --> 09:31.622
Hey, Barry.

09:32.656 --> 09:34.491
Kim, David.

09:35.726 --> 09:36.959
Did you see the review?

09:39.295 --> 09:40.129
Yep.

09:42.098 --> 09:43.099
Can't win 'em all.

09:45.168 --> 09:46.002
Nope.

09:47.771 --> 09:50.605
We're uh, we're gonna, we're
just gonna get outta your hair,

09:50.607 --> 09:52.973
let you have the
space to prepare.

09:52.975 --> 09:54.308
Thanks.

09:54.310 --> 09:58.012
Oh, look, fuck that
guy, am I right?

09:58.014 --> 09:59.348
- Yeah.
- Right.

09:59.350 --> 10:00.351
No, no no.

10:02.952 --> 10:04.120
Fuck that guy.

10:07.290 --> 10:08.457
Yeah.

10:08.459 --> 10:09.957
Break a leg.

10:09.959 --> 10:12.095
Where'd she, uh, where'd she go?

10:19.936 --> 10:20.868
Hi, are you Tom?

10:20.870 --> 10:22.038
- Yep, Phyllis?
- Yes.

10:25.041 --> 10:26.340
Thank you.

10:26.342 --> 10:27.778
- No problem, headin' south?
- Yessir.

10:46.996 --> 10:50.131
I've been very
into manifesting, lately.

10:50.133 --> 10:51.800
What's that?

10:51.802 --> 10:54.503
Manifesting,
like vision boards?

10:54.505 --> 10:57.304
It's all about the
laws of attraction.

10:57.306 --> 10:59.841
There's this higher
plane of existence,

10:59.843 --> 11:02.209
where your desires
are not just a wish,

11:02.211 --> 11:05.547
but they're actually reality.

11:05.549 --> 11:08.850
Identifying your visions,
and giving them clarity,

11:08.852 --> 11:12.353
and then focusing
on that clarity,

11:12.355 --> 11:14.890
will manifest what you
truly want in life.

11:14.892 --> 11:17.526
If you refuse the outside
world, and prevent it

11:17.528 --> 11:20.027
from distracting you
from your intentions,

11:20.029 --> 11:22.533
you can achieve
anything you want.

11:23.734 --> 11:25.334
That's how I got this part.

11:26.437 --> 11:29.038
That sounds like bullshit.

11:30.273 --> 11:31.274
It's not.

11:32.443 --> 11:35.744
I read it in a
book, and it works.

11:35.746 --> 11:37.211
That's how I got this part.

11:37.213 --> 11:39.046
You got this part
because you were sl...

11:39.048 --> 11:44.084
Right, well, I wanna
congratulate everybody,

11:44.086 --> 11:46.555
on a very successful run.

11:46.557 --> 11:49.223
Speech!

11:49.225 --> 11:54.197
Um, I know some of you have
probably read the reviews,

11:55.364 --> 12:00.269
