I'm proud of you.

12:04.641 --> 12:09.078
In a time when space is limited,
it's, you know, hey, hey,

12:13.650 --> 12:15.983
♪ All the world is but a stage ♪

12:23.494 --> 12:26.930
Life, life is a performance.

12:29.465 --> 12:30.634
