13:21.685 --> 13:25.554
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

14:10.266 --> 14:11.100
How's this?

14:12.903 --> 14:14.268
Great.

14:14.270 --> 14:16.236
Do I look like a
relaxed and friendly guy?

14:16.238 --> 14:17.204
Yes.

14:17.206 --> 14:19.009
