14:20.176 --> 14:21.408
Yes.

14:21.410 --> 14:22.244
Good.

14:34.223 --> 14:35.025
Barry?

14:39.029 --> 14:40.931
- Stand on the X.
- Yeah.

14:46.202 --> 14:49.070
