17:09.946 --> 17:10.847
You're Phyllis.

17:11.915 --> 17:13.514
Yep.

17:13.516 --> 17:15.518
Hm, thought it was that lady.

17:20.190 --> 17:21.256
No.

17:21.258 --> 17:22.225
You're an artist?

17:23.292 --> 17:24.127
