you want them to mean.

17:49.752 --> 17:50.586
That's art.

17:52.956 --> 17:55.924
What does art mean to you?

17:55.926 --> 18:00.831
Well, good art is an expression,
where you share the world

18:03.599 --> 18:08.303
to someone in a way that,
maybe they've known, but um,

18:08.305 --> 18:09.738
never really experienced.

18:13.475 --> 18:16.079
Have you experienced the
world in a way I haven't?

18:20.183 --> 18:22.683
I don't, I don't know.

18:22.685 --> 18:24.185
Okay.

18:24.187 --> 18:25.856
Well, bye.

18:43.772 --> 18:45.439
Stop eating so much cheese.

18:45.441 --> 18:47.610
I can eat as much
cheese as I wanna eat.

