No.

1:11:11.318 --> 1:11:14.087
Every time we go anywhere, the
world as we know it changes.

1:11:16.189 --> 1:11:18.425
We should just be happy
with what we've got.

1:11:21.328 --> 1:11:22.329
I'm staying right here.

1:11:27.034 --> 1:11:28.268
